OL,3,CUrgent manhunt underway after 'high-
OL,4,Crisk' prisoner escapes from hospital
OL,6,FAn urgent manhunt is underway for a
OL,7,F"high risk" prisoner who has absconded
OL,8,Ffrom custody while being treated at a
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FMarwan Jumaa, who is currently serving
OL,12,Fa sentence for assaulting two women,
OL,13,Fescaped after being transferred from a
OL,14,Fsecure hospital facility to North
OL,15,FManchester Hospital for medical
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police have warned
OL,19,Fthe public that the 20-year-old man is
OL,20,Fdeemed to be a risk to both himself
OL,21,Fand others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
