PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784281689
OL,3,CUrgent manhunt underway after 'high-
OL,4,Crisk' prisoner escapes from hospital
OL,6,FHe is black, of skinny build with
OL,7,Fshort, dark hair, and approximately
OL,8,F5ft 10 inches.
OL,10,FJumaa is known to have connections in
OL,11,Fseveral parts of the country including
OL,12,FBury, Prestwich, Crumpsall, Leeds and
OL,13,FLondon.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Abigail
OL,16,FCronin, from Greater Manchester
OL,17,FPolice, reassured the local community
OL,18,Fthat a dedicated team is actively
OL,19,Fsearching for Jumaa.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
