OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784281689
OL,3,CUrgent manhunt underway after 'high-
OL,4,Crisk' prisoner escapes from hospital
OL,6,F"We are urging anybody to come forward
OL,7,Fwho may have information about
OL,8,FMarwan's whereabouts," DCI Cronin said.
OL,10,F"I recognise that this may heighten
OL,11,Fconcern within the community. However,
OL,12,FI want to assure you that we have
OL,13,Fofficers working around the clock to
OL,14,Ffind Marwan and return him to hospital
OL,15,Fas soon as possible.
OL,17,F"If sighted, do not approach him,
OL,18,Fplease call 999 immediately."
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
